Package jx.compiler.execenv

Class BCMethod

java.lang.Object
jx.compiler.execenv.BCMethod
Direct Known Subclasses:
BCMethodWithCode
public class BCMethod extends Object
This class represents a Java method without its bytecode. If you need a Java method with bytecode (e.g. for translating it), take the subclass of BCMethod, BCMethodWithCode. This class is used for tasks where the code isn't required, e.g. for testing if a method is 'inlineable'.
